  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        Ostomy patients who:

          -  Have healthy peristomal skin

          -  Are within 12 weeks post op

        Exclusion Criteria:

        Ostomy patients who:

          -  Have a fistula, wound, lesion or suspected infection in the peristomal area

          -  Are in-patient in healthcare facility
      </textblock>
